---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about the New Hope Creek Watershed organization and our mission.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-earth font-bold mb-8 text-center">About Us</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-earth/80">
      <p>
        The New Hope Creek Watershed organization is dedicated to the protection, 
        preservation, and restoration of the New Hope Creek watershed in Durham, North Carolina.
      </p>
      
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        A thriving watershed where healthy streams, protected forests, and engaged 
        communities come together to safeguard our natural resources for generations to come.
      </p>
      
      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Monitor water quality throughout the watershed</li>
        <li>Coordinate stream cleanup and restoration projects</li>
        <li>Advocate for policies that protect our waterways</li>
        <li>Educate the community about watershed stewardship</li>
        <li>Partner with local organizations and government agencies</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>The Watershed</h2>
      <p>
        New Hope Creek flows through Durham and Orange counties before joining 
        Jordan Lake. The watershed includes numerous tributaries and encompasses 
        diverse habitats including forests, wetlands, and urban streams.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-creek-50 rounded-lg border border-creek-200 text-center">
        <p class="text-earth/60 italic mb-0">
          More information coming soon. <a href="/contact" class="text-creek-600 hover:underline">Get in touch</a> to learn how you can help.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
